                      Directory Contents - doc/settings


  core.settings

    Documentation for core Eggdrop configuration settings. Covers bot
    identity, servers, channels, networking, TLS/SSL, security, logging,
    file paths, and behavior settings. All settings are shown in TOML
    format (the recommended configuration format).

  mod.assoc

    Documentation for the assoc module. Provides party-line channel naming
    and aliasing support.

  mod.blowfish

    Documentation for the blowfish module. Provides legacy blowfish
    password encryption support (consider using PBKDF2 for new
    installations).

  mod.channels

    Documentation for the channels module. Provides channel tracking,
    management, and per-channel configuration.

  mod.compress

    Documentation for the compress module. Provides zlib compression for
    userfile transfers over botnet links.

  mod.console

    Documentation for the console module. Provides persistent DCC console
    settings across bot restarts.

  mod.ctcp

    Documentation for the ctcp module. Provides CTCP functionality and
    customizable CTCP responses.

  mod.dns

    Documentation for the dns module. Provides asynchronous DNS resolution
    with caching.

  mod.filesys

    Documentation for the filesys module. Provides built-in file server
    functionality with upload/download support.

  mod.ident

    Documentation for the ident module. Provides ident daemon support
    for proper IRC username identification.

  mod.irc

    Documentation for the irc module. Provides core IRC protocol support
    and mode/ban handling.

  mod.notes

    Documentation for the notes module. Provides note storage for offline
    users.

  mod.seen

    Documentation for the seen module. Provides basic !seen command
    functionality.

  mod.server

    Documentation for the server module. Provides core IRC server
    connection support and SASL authentication.

  mod.share

    Documentation for the share module. Provides userfile sharing with
    linked bots on the botnet.

  mod.transfer

    Documentation for the transfer module. Provides DCC SEND/GET and
    userfile transfer support.

  mod.uptime

    Documentation for the uptime module. Provides uptime reporting to
    https://www.eggheads.org/uptime/

  mod.woobie

    Documentation for the woobie module. Provides WooBIE protocol support
    for backwards compatibility.

